{"tid":590144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所以話吹奏新移民真係弱智","createTime":"2018-03-12T11:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T06:37:00.000Z","uid":39796,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2a5114c9df491b3e762c5ce328c4498e302373a2","tid":590144,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:03:35.000Z","msg":"泛民咁多年吹奏新移民人士<br />\n話要民主感化佢地<br />\n點知投票就自己拎石頭掉自己隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一班香港人吹捧<br />\n人地肯番工肯講廣東話就應接受佢地<br />\n<br />\n你睇下姚松炎輸邊到<br />\n一到投票就投番保蝗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa545932f818b4b4200330631e3be55824926a71","tid":590144,"uid":38778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:04:30.000Z","msg":"咁醒就唔叫泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d198140bc68ff5ab5937f4e1cb0f428b222d15c4","tid":590144,"uid":42921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:06:11.000Z","msg":"2020又多8萬新移民票，真係想要幾多票都得"},{"pid":"37afed2176d3fdf48ffac742576ee8108b449b6a","tid":590144,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁醒就唔叫泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有一批香港人助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6b33eeafb2bcef8cac5f0d799ebe4ce72cb006","tid":590144,"uid":53705,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"歐洲左膠 更加弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地以為對 中東難民好.........D中東難民 就會感恩<br />\n<br />\n點知中東難民 反而得吋進尺, 係歐洲又搶劫, 又強姦, 又恐襲, 又強逼歐洲人一齊信伊斯蘭教"},{"pid":"dde75ff966b0195e8953ad107308819b41fa0735","tid":590144,"uid":53705,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"37afed2176d3fdf48ffac742576ee8108b449b6a","tid":590144,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime